%% Data Flow Diagram - Notebooks (Workbench Images)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant NotebookCtrl as odh-notebook-controller
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Image Deployment
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Kustomize overlay<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ImageStreams created
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Resolve ImageStream tags<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull Secret
    Registry-->>K8sAPI: Image manifests (SHA256)
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Read ImageStream annotations<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Available workbench images

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 2: Workbench Pod Lifecycle
    User->>Dashboard: Select workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, OAuth
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Notebook CR event
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod + Service + HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull Secret
    Registry-->>K8sAPI: Container image layers
    User->>KubeRBAC: Access workbench<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KubeRBAC->>Workbench: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8888, localhost

    Note over K8sAPI,Registry: Flow 3: RStudio On-Cluster Build
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: BuildConfig triggered
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull base image<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull Secret
    Registry-->>K8sAPI: Base image layers
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Build RStudio image
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Push to ImageStreamTag
